## 📊 Google Sheets – Student Engagement Tracker

- Built a centralized tracker to monitor student performance and engagement across batches  
- Tracked key metrics: attendance %, penalties, academic performance, grievances, and project participation  
- Implemented logic to auto-flag “at-risk” students based on performance and engagement signals  
- Defined KPI monitoring with weekly (early warning) and monthly (outcome) reviews  
- Structured accountability across stakeholders (Ops, Faculty, Program Leads)  

